sentences: She has also played guitar in the bands Even Worse (in which she was also the singer), Chop Shop, Hit by a Truck, Missing Foundation, Pussy Galore, Madgodz, Bubba Zanetti (NYC), Sloth, Hellvis (NYC), the Floyds of Flatbush, the Wharton Tiers Ensemble and Judas Livingston Seagull, and bass in the bands Big Stick, Navigator and Verona Downs.
Currently she plays bass with Carvels NYC and Bush Tetras, and sometimes sits in with Brooklyn-based band Um.
Korbet contributed a track in 2020 to Marc Sloan's Reel To Real vol.
